(5. CORE PRODUCT VALUE) Tj
T*
(1. Revenue protection:) Tj
T*
(strict payment gate prevents unpaid printing.) Tj
T*
(2. Operational reliability:) Tj
T*
(daily operator command pack and retry-safe payment flow.) Tj
T*
(3. Customer clarity:) Tj
T*
(status timeline and receipt endpoints for frontend UX.) Tj
T*
(4. Local resilience:) Tj
T*
(Pi-local runtime keeps kiosk usable even without full cloud dependency.) Tj
T*
(5. Auditability:) Tj
T*
(transaction references, job states, and reports available for management.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(6. CURRENT TECHNICAL ARCHITECTURE) Tj
T*
(1. Backend:) Tj
T*
(FastAPI + PostgreSQL.) Tj
T*
(2. Edge runtime:) Tj
T*
(Raspberry Pi + systemd services + CUPS printer integration.) Tj
T*
(3. Payment:) Tj
T*
(provider integration with reconcile support for delayed confirmations.) Tj
T*
(4. Customer and admin web apps:) Tj
T*
(served locally from backend \(`/customer-app`, `/admin-app`\).) Tj
T*
(5. Deployment model:) Tj
T*
(local-first kiosk operation with optional cloud/public webhook access.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(7. LOCAL-FIRST STRATEGY \(IMPORTANT FOR SCALE AND COST\)) Tj
T*
(The system is intentionally designed to run as much as possible on each Pi:) Tj
T*
(1. API service on Pi.) Tj
T*
(2. Database on Pi.) Tj
T*
(3. Print agent on Pi.) Tj
T*
(4. Printer queue and driver layer on Pi.) Tj
T*
(5. Customer UI hosted on Pi local network.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Cloud/external services are used only where necessary:) Tj
T*
(1. Payment provider APIs \(Snippe/Mixx\).) Tj
T*
(2. Mobile network infrastructure.) Tj
T*
(3. Optional public webhook ingress and remote admin access.) Tj
T*
(4. Source backup/collaboration via GitHub.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(8. SECURITY AND CONTROL PRINCIPLES) Tj
T*
(1. Non-negotiable gate:) Tj
T*
(No successful payment => no printing.) Tj
T*
(2. Retry-safe payment creation to avoid accidental duplicate charges.) Tj
T*
(3. Provider-reference based reconciliation and incident handling.) Tj
T*
(4. Customer contract versioning \(`v1`\) to keep frontend stable.) Tj
T*
(5. Controlled file handling:) Tj
T*
(uploaded files are temporary, with cleanup after print success and stale file TTL cleanup.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(9. MULTI-KIOSK READINESS) Tj
T*
(The platform already includes multi-kiosk provisioning foundation:) Tj
T*
(1. Kiosk profile template per site.) Tj
ET
endstream
endobj
