T*
(   - `/admin/reports/today`) Tj
T*
(   - `/admin/pricing`) Tj
T*
(   - `/alerts`) Tj
T*
(2. Customer APIs delivered and contract-frozen:) Tj
T*
(   - `/print-jobs/{job_id}/customer-status`) Tj
T*
(   - `/print-jobs/{job_id}/customer-receipt`) Tj
T*
(3. Automated backend regression suite established and passing.) Tj
T*
(4. Payment retry-safe flow and provider reference snapshot checks implemented.) Tj
T*
(5. Customer flow UI implemented with:) Tj
T*
(   - auto page detection,) Tj
T*
(   - one-mode-at-a-time selection,) Tj
T*
(   - custom page range support,) Tj
T*
(   - default hidden payment method \(M-Pesa\),) Tj
T*
(   - server-side anti-cheat billing enforcement.) Tj
T*
(6. Local deployment and smoke validation on Pi completed.) Tj
T*
