T*
(11. BUSINESS IMPACT POTENTIAL) Tj
T*
(1. New unattended or low-attended print revenue channels.) Tj
T*
(2. Standardized customer experience across branches.) Tj
T*
(3. Reduced fraud/leakage from manual payment handling.) Tj
T*
(4. Better reporting for finance and decision-making.) Tj
T*
(5. Faster expansion to schools, institutions, and public service points.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(12. EXPANSION PATH) Tj
T*
