T*
(single-kiosk hardening and production discipline.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Phase 2:) Tj
T*
(multi-kiosk rollout with centralized monitoring.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Phase 3:) Tj
T*
(optional central cloud control plane and analytics for cross-site intelligence.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(13. INVESTOR PERSPECTIVE) Tj
T*
(Hasnet PrintHub is not only a software project; it is an operational platform for distributed) Tj
T*
(revenue points.) Tj
T*
(Its strength is the combination of:) Tj
T*
(1. hard payment-control policy,) Tj
T*
(2. practical field operations tooling,) Tj
